e.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"137d208cb0f50b54a7d42a74ba43ed9897a8c4a3","tid":921753,"uid":22465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9fa90eceaae3af461d6a781f4cbed9d365e37fdd","tid":921753,"uid":112161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6acd3db7a61ccf19f1f1e53a3b5bc18334e0f9ab","tid":921753,"uid":83782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T13:15:55.000Z","msg":"證券化左既貸款利息係咪會小過銀行自己收既利息？定證卷既價錢會高過9000蚊，銀行就可以食個差價？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T13:27:04.000Z","msg":"理論上你講果兩項都係可行<br />\n實際要睇睇書先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T12:55:41.000Z","msg":"要睇市況同埋underlying asset係乜，資產靚既銀行可以有premium咁賣出去，但有時做證券化個陣會有discount賣資產既情況出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef3337561faaeae6f2af55ea2ac238f5a3068788","tid":921753,"uid":87737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e26f5ae417ea432ce16f41d15ed9695476a20f36","tid":921753,"uid":139027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T12:49:43.000Z","msg":"巴打，我想乜都唔識，完全係一個新手。想學識由零到買股票或者其他金融衍生產品，應該從何學起？或者有咩書係適合新手睇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T13:30:41.000Z","msg":"咩原因令你想接觸金融產品<br />\n同埋你本身財政有幾充裕先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96ca8bf3849606c191e0c751fa1202eb9871b14b","tid":921753,"uid":139027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T13:32:54.000Z","msg":"只係一個學生哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇錢<br />\n<br />\n但係我覺得遲早都要接觸投資呢方面，早啲起步就比其他人更多經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ae4e78403dcd2c68e2c04ad3304b03397faadb4","tid":921753,"uid":87737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"96ca8bf3849606c191e0c751fa1202eb9871b14b","tid":921753,"uid":139027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T13:32:54.000Z","msg":"只係一個學生哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇錢<br />\n<br />\n但係我覺得遲早都要接觸投資呢方面，早啲起步就比其他人更多經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T13:43:12.000Z","msg":"如果你相信我嘅，我想勸你唔好考慮通過金融搵快錢<br />\n好多人都好早就接觸金融產品<br />\n但到中年、老年都仲好窮<br />\n就係因為逃不出炒賣嘅迷思<br />\n<br />\n我係其中一個，畢業幾年前後輸咗廿幾萬<br />\n當然對好多巴打，呢啲唔係大錢<br />\n但對我，係平日好省先有一舊錢可以再投入個市場<br />\n幾多次見到靚衫、貴餐廳想買想試唔捨得<br />\n諗住留嚟有個好將來<br />\n呢種想法下輸輸吓，會問自己到底省嚟為咩<br />\n<br />\n呢個世界，只有輸咗唔志在嘅人<br />\n兩個可能性（錢係客嘅/幾十萬未開頭）<br />\n係做到靠炒賣致富<br />\n其他嘅，就算短期贏咗，最後都只會上得山多終遇虎"},{"pid":"f6006ea4b8eca8c133cfd085e7edb835de41cf39","tid":921753,"uid":49707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T13:54:51.000Z","msg":"留名學野"},{"pid":"8cee1419c0bde4056a4e35fbfeccf9ef36af4dd9","tid":921753,"uid":49707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27e5c84332537c302201d7a9b61fd97c8762bf31","tid":921753,"uid":112161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e506e0f430045f3ba802205c96983f04e6526d8b","tid":921753,"uid":117974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T11:45:44.000Z","msg":"唔關呢個post事 但巴打我想問你係點幫隻股估值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T11:59:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n目前主要用股息率+現金流折現"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T13:56:19.000Z","msg":"你會點定個discount rate"},{"pid":"6d698ae8c525046aefe9c0556c073db9bb3b1aba","tid":921753,"uid":150730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T14:11:30.000Z","msg":"之前好似話佢地用開 Gaussian Copula 黎price CDO 所以爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"},{"pid":"e6994f2d3a19be59f0df02975bb4d6a33804b456","tid":921753,"uid":89316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T14:14:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/a